      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L in poor condition. The engine and/or mechanical systems have notable issues that will require attention. The interior shows significant wear, including staining, damage, or deterioration beyond normal use. The exterior has visible scratches, dents, or other cosmetic damage. This vehicle is best suited for buyers comfortable with a project car or willing to invest in repairs.",
